  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Persons with COPD are randomized to pedometer versus pedometer plus Internet mediated
      website to promote walking and physical activity.  Primary outcome is 6-minute walk test
      distance.  Intervention lasts 3 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
